description:

elements.name: 2.1 Originator creating Bridge Pre close loan using excel file with valid assignment fee in it

steps.name: user is on login page
"originator" enter the valid credentials and click on sign in button
user should see the dashboard page
user will click on Proceed button
user will select loan type as "Bridge"
user will select loan stage as "Pre close"
user will upload data tape for "Rehab Bridge" loan
user is on loan page

steps.name: user is on login page

user should see the dashboard page
user will click on Proceed button
user will select loan type as "Bridge"
user will select loan stage as "Pre close"
user will upload data tape for "Bridge" loan "without" assignment fees
user is on loan page
user validates the assignment fees field error

steps.name: user is on login page

user should see the dashboard page

user will select loan type as "DSCR"

user will upload data tape for "DSCR" loan "without" assignment fees
